{"tid":2386993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國小鎮二戰救過猶太人 驚喜獲贈6800萬元遺產","createTime":"2021-01-30T03:34:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T04:31:52.000Z","uid":28114,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9d0aa224e7992eb676fab58e79660baf23fd5740","tid":2386993,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T03:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/01/30/phpWBRHTQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F01%2F30%2FphpWBRHTQ.jpg&h=8df1d4c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法國小鎮利尼翁河畔勒尚邦（Le Chambon-sur-Lignon，圖），在二戰期間曾庇護成千上萬的猶太人，1名當年曾逃難到此的90歲老翁施瓦姆（Eric Sc​​hwam）過世後，遺囑交代要將財產分給小鎮，預估有200萬歐元（約新台幣6800萬元）之譜。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/novelty/breakingnews/3426901\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fnovelty%2Fbreakingnews%2F3426901&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VHzcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=147f865a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fnovelty%2Fbreakingnews%2F3426901&h=06caed28\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/novelty/breakingnews/3426901</a><br />\n<br />\n2021/01/30 09:44<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕法國小鎮利尼翁河畔勒尚邦（Le Chambon-sur-Lignon），於第二次世界大戰期間曾庇護過成千上萬的猶太人，讓他們免遭納粹德國毒手，一名當年曾和家人一起逃難到此的90歲老翁施瓦姆（Eric Sc​​hwam）上個月過世，遺囑交代要將財產分給小鎮，預估有200萬歐元（約新台幣6800萬元）之譜。<br />\n<br />\n據《BBC》報導，來自於奧地利維也納的施瓦姆，二戰時曾被關進法國南部的里韋薩爾泰（Rivesaltes）營地，1943年和父母、祖父母一起抵達了利尼翁河畔勒尚邦，平安度過戰爭後，施瓦姆1950年移居里昂學習藥學。<br />\n<br />\n這個法國小鎮居民雖然只有2500人左右，但早在17世紀就曾保護過遭受宗教迫害的新教徒。二戰期間，小鎮牧師和妻子出面呼籲大家協助猶太難民避難，以免他們被納粹德國和其扶植的維琪法國政權所殘害，鎮上居民隨即有力出力，收留了到處逃難的猶太人，其善舉如今也被以色列認證。<br />\n<br />\n鎮長艾羅德（Jean-Michel Eyraud）證實了收到遺產捐贈的消息，但並未透露詳細數字，僅表示這筆錢會用在教育和資助青年活動上面。不過，前任鎮長在幾年前曾表示，施瓦姆詢問捐款事宜時提到的金額達到200萬歐元。"},{"pid":"aa7c03ae89de6d9018ac7826187474f67b169d9e","tid":2386993,"uid":36383,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T03:36:08.000Z","msg":"救香港人嘅話可獲工作面試機會"},{"pid":"a6d7c1453addc9edd227ef6ecbbe22a2712177d4","tid":2386993,"uid":81365,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T03:41:10.000Z","msg":"希魔撞正殺人狂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42fa2a743e9de7cdcd43dcbb9b439d629b2beb2b","tid":2386993,"uid":52358,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T03:43:56.000Z","msg":"捐糧捐物資返中国<br />\n40年後同你講<br />\n要不是中央你們香港完蛋了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f510e37ec065e952b75a7314af32caba5f3ebe","tid":2386993,"uid":33422,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"42fa2a743e9de7cdcd43dcbb9b439d629b2beb2b","tid":2386993,"uid":52358,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T03:43:56.000Z","msg":"捐糧捐物資返中国<br />\n40年後同你講<br />\n要不是中央你們香港完蛋了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T03:49:06.000Z","msg":"支那人不嬲自卑到會恩將仇報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89fb0a14f7a55ca32e429247fb9da4684c2144f3","tid":2386993,"uid":49588,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"42fa2a743e9de7cdcd43dcbb9b439d629b2beb2b","tid":2386993,"uid":52358,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T03:43:56.000Z","msg":"捐糧捐物資返中国<br />\n40年後同你講<br />\n要不是中央你們香港完蛋了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T03:56:03.000Z","msg":"現在還更改歷史<br />\n<br />\n把恩人，受助人角色對調"},{"pid":"412ded887f15639ef6a1702b60f38de2c3152c39","tid":2386993,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T04:31:52.000Z","msg":"好在唔係救中國人<br />\n救完下一步就比人鬥土豪分田地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}